\left(\int_0^1 |g(x)|\cdot 1\ dx\right)^2\leq \int_0^1 g^2(x)\ dx \int_0^1 1^2\ dx<\infty
A = \{x: |g(x)| \geq 1\}
 \begin{align*} \int_{0}^{1} |g(x)| \, dx &= \int_{A} |g(x)|\, dx + \int_{(0,1)-A} |g(x)|\, dx \\ &\leq \int_{A} |g(x)|^{2}\, dx + \int_{(0,1)-A} |g(x)|\, dx \\ &\leq \int_{0}^{1} |g(x)|^{2}\, dx + 1 \\ &< \infty. \end{align*} 
